definitions.definition: To sharply poke or pinch the buttocks, or prod between the buttocks, of (a person).
To gently accelerate (an automobile or machine), or give repeated small taps on the accelerator.
Of private-hire taxi drivers, to pick up a passenger who has not booked a cab, in violation of UK licensing conditions.
To hiss (a performer) off the stage.

main_definition: ( transitive , slang ) To sharply poke or pinch the buttocks, or prod between the buttocks, of (a person).
secondary_definitions: ( transitive , slang ) To stimulate ; to spur .
( transitive , slang ) To gently accelerate (an automobile or machine), or give repeated small taps on the accelerator.
( slang , UK ) Of private-hire taxi drivers, to pick up a passenger who has not booked a cab, in violation of UK licensing conditions.
( transitive , slang ) To hiss (a performer) off the stage.
